                                  UFW
                                  ---

1. Introduction
----------------

The ufw template enables UFW (Uncomplicated Firewall) support in
the kernel and adds the ufw package to the image.

2. Usage
--------

The recipe will throw warning info about supported architectures, if it is being
built on supported arch, just ignore the warning.

Add this template to your configure line:
 --templates feature/ufw

This will ensure the required kernel config values are set.

3. Installation
----------------

This template will include ufw in the root filesystem. No additional installation
steps are required.
